00:03:14.870 --> 00:03:18.320
that this animal faced,
and in turn, can help us

00:03:18.320 --> 00:03:22.543
understand what changed
in our lineage and why.

00:03:23.870 --> 00:03:26.207
Both chimpanzees and bonobos eat meat.

