that chimps gain a lot of
nutrition from hunting,

00:51:14.810 --> 00:51:17.420
but I think perhaps the
more interesting question

00:51:17.420 --> 00:51:20.130
is why females don't
hunt more at other sites.

00:51:20.130 --> 00:51:23.070
And Ian talked about some
of these issues as well,

